enhanced_by.method_name: predicatedSortedMap(SortedMap<K, V>, Predicate<? super K>, Predicate<? super V>)
enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve creating a new PredicatedSortedMap instance with a SortedMap and predicates.
Both methods return a subset of the original map, making them functionally similar.
Validation of keys and values is required before any map operations, including tailMap.
Adding elements to the map may affect the result of tailMap, so put should be tested in conjunction.
